---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - ThangQT" description="About me and what I do">
  <section class="col-main">
    <h2 style="font-size: var(--fs-body-m); margin-bottom: var(--margin);">About Me</h2>
    
    <p>
      I'm a designer and developer with a passion for creating beautiful, 
      functional web experiences. With over X years in the industry, I've 
      worked with startups, agencies, and Fortune 500 companies.
    </p>
    
    <p>
      My approach combines clean design principles with modern technology 
      to build products that people love to use. I believe in thoughtful 
      interactions, accessible interfaces, and code that's as elegant as 
      the designs it powers.
    </p>
    
    <h2 style="font-size: var(--fs-body-m); margin-top: calc(var(--margin) * 2); margin-bottom: var(--margin);">
      What I Do
    </h2>
    
    <p>
      I specialize in frontend development, design systems, and creative 
      coding. My toolkit includes React, TypeScript, Astro, and modern 
      CSS. I'm also experienced in design tools like Figma and have a 
      strong foundation in UX principles.
    </p>
    
    <p>
      When I'm not coding or designing, you'll find me exploring new 
      technologies, contributing to open source, or writing about web 
      development on my blog.
    </p>
    
    <h2 style="font-size: var(--fs-body-m); margin-top: calc(var(--margin) * 2); margin-bottom: var(--margin);">
      Let's Connect
    </h2>
    
    <p>
      I'm always interested in hearing about new projects and opportunities. 
      Feel free to reach out via <a href="mailto:your@email.com">email</a> or 
      connect with me on <a href="https://github.com/yourusername" target="_blank">GitHub</a> 
      and <a href="https://twitter.com/yourusername" target="_blank">Twitter</a>.
    </p>
  </section>

  <aside class="col-sidebar">
    <div class="is-visible">
      <h2>About</h2>
    </div>
  </aside>
</Layout>
